            <title>[LU-1788] osc_brw_redo_request() shouldn&apos;t print a message to console when retrying because of EINPROGRESS</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1788</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;EINPROGRESS can now legitemately be returned during normal operation (e.g. quota rebalancing is in progress), so we shouldn&apos;t print an error message on client each time a retry is done due to EINPROGRESS.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
